{"tid":542244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"chenglap：這世界上最不欠缺的資源叫人類","createTime":"2018-01-27T09:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T13:33:39.000Z","uid":47714,"like":37,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e9e0fc75428da48e9b7683a85c332b6487b5e2","tid":542244,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T09:38:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155954259452357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10155954259452357&d=7OokyB%2F3QRM7rQz4CQKcnp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=09d41039\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10155954259452357</a><br />\n<br />\n如果我是共產黨, 你要投共, 我真的不明白為何我不消滅你而對一直就忠於我的人好一點, 而要對你好? 在中國那麼過億人從四歲開始就忠於共產黨, 他們比你們這些香港人還要窮, 誰要你那種去到三十歲甚至五十歲混得不好才來投共的?<br />\n<br />\n「對長期忠於自己的人好一點」不是常識嗎? 要當狗, 也要能發揮狗的用途, 何況你不是他養的唐狗, 而是一隻被遺棄的狗.<br />\n<br />\n如果你帶巨富來投, 帶著我需要而沒有的技術, 你還有一點收買的價值, 但在收買價值用完後還是必須消滅. 一無所有的人覺得自己有權投共, 是不是想太多? 如果不為爭取自己的生存和力量, 他們剩下的唯一選擇不是投共, 是消滅.<br />\n<br />\n少一個人, 少一雙筷子, 少一個失業者, 少一份綜援, 少一個退休負擔, 醫院少一個人排隊, 少需要一個公屋單位, 這世界上最不欠缺的資源叫人類. 有些時候人類的價值還比不上一件蛋糕, 因為人類的價值可以是負數.<br />\n<br />\n幻想移民跟幻想能投共, 本質上是一樣的, 就是以為自己有路可走, 去面對那個根本無路可走的現實."},{"pid":"ef8f8d6bb2fa8700302551565c51a93464f5d67a","tid":542244,"uid":80788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"冇窮人邊個幫有錢人做哂d下賤工夫等有錢人可以享受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算蛋糕都要有蛋糕師傅整出黎,唔通d蛋糕識自己生出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c68a676794297338e8e4f3dd877e7bab9aa375","tid":542244,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:04:00.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"0b4fd3b83e1b3a6f8ce7e96fb0be5033d94bd8bc","tid":542244,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef8f8d6bb2fa8700302551565c51a93464f5d67a","tid":542244,"uid":80788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"冇窮人邊個幫有錢人做哂d下賤工夫等有錢人可以享受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算蛋糕都要有蛋糕師傅整出黎,唔通d蛋糕識自己生出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:04:17.000Z","msg":"中國o既窮人　佢地自己大把　要幾賤有幾賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96be8dea44d0b99c5e7ed0affdf14403c0d45db","tid":542244,"uid":61462,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T10:11:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/180704_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F180704_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=a9795c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/180831_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F180831_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=74e9b67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n溫兆倫<br />\n<br />\n真係氓過屎嘅廁紙"},{"pid":"0b8c5d6bf29706a63e78d12af33795125c229178","tid":542244,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"其實全球化o既問題　好多人講過　而且全球化唔係人類歷史第一次"},{"pid":"7c9c2b701a9fb8d45c3e1fe43d139197da9a6031","tid":542244,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b8c5d6bf29706a63e78d12af33795125c229178","tid":542244,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"其實全球化o既問題　好多人講過　而且全球化唔係人類歷史第一次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T11:57:20.000Z","msg":"蒙古人到處屠城<br />\n奴隸夠用就得"},{"pid":"531357ae3acfcbf30bd77a2ba6852aa6e96b8415","tid":542244,"uid":25055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T12:08:47.000Z","msg":"未來幾十年會唔會黎個經濟大洗牌？<br />\n而家根本全球貧富懸殊得好嚴重"},{"pid":"60a1efab79f5184631b7318736efe6a41e99