:01:39.000Z","msg":"全球化係因為科技進步　科技唔會變　但係政治會變<br />\n未有火車之前　世界各國o既邊境唔係似得當代咁<br />\n宜家世界各國邊界咁硬　係由工業革命產生火車呢類科技暴發增長後出現"},{"pid":"5bafbd4a5e5c43b22fba0203cc6a7fda8c6be407","tid":542244,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T10:20:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">有些時候人類的價值還比不上一件蛋糕, 因為人類的價值可以是負數.</span><br />\n<br />\n想起狄志遠同黃成智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又想選議員，選唔到又想入政府做官<br />\n支援袋住先同國教，但根本無人想理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6329b87636c7350177d713a12971cccb66388b1","tid":542244,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>war係要攬炒，唔係要變富有<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n可以無視"}]}